	<h3>Upload Progress Widget</h3>
	<p>
		The Upload Progress widget is a temporary widget that will appear on the
		screen if the user has selected multiple photos to be uploaded to the app.
		This widget will display all the photos that are being uploaded, and will
		inform the user if there has been an error in the upload and allow them to
		try it again. I included intuitive graphics in the design to indicate when a
		photo was either uploading or if it failed to upload due to an error.
	</p>
</div>
