	<h3>Job Pipeline Widget</h3>
	<p>
		The Job Pipeline widget displays the number of jobs that are currently in
		each phase of the job process. By tapping one of the letter graphics on the
		screen, the user can quickly filter their job search to a specific phase.
		The widget displays the sum of all job balances in each phase, as well as
		the total number of jobs. This gives users a quick overview of all the jobs
		that are currently active.
	</p>
</div>
