<div class="container portfolio-container processGrp">
	<h3>Calendar Widget</h3>
	<p>
		The Calendar widget shows users their top five upcoming events. Once the top
		event occurs, the widget updates by replacing the ongoing event with a new
		upcoming event, if available. The widget includes a few quick actions that
		allow the user to add a new event and view the entire calendar. The calendar
		also organizes the events into three categories: Labor Order, Material
		Order, and Appointments.
	</p>
</div>
